---

ExifTool Notice:

This software requires ExifTool to be installed separately. ExifTool is a 
platform-independent Perl application for reading, writing and editing meta 
information in a wide variety of files. ExifTool is developed and maintained 
by Phil Harvey and is available under the Perl Artistic License or GPL.

For more information about ExifTool:
- Homepage: https://exiftool.org/
- Documentation: https://exiftool.org/ExifTool.html
- Source Code: https://github.com/exiftool/exiftool

