Disclaimer:

This software processes media files and their metadata. While every effort has
been made to ensure data safety and integrity, users are strongly advised to:

1. Create backups of important files before processing
2. Test the software on non-critical data first
3. Verify results before relying on processed data
4. Understand that metadata modification is irreversible in some cases

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any data
loss, corruption, or other damages that may result from the use of this software.
Use at your own risk and always maintain proper backups.